casebody.data:
Janice and Jeff GRAY, Individually and as Parents and Next Friends of J.G., Plaintiffs-Appellees,
v.
James Lee HOHENSHELL, Defendant-Appellant. No. 17-1100 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 23, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

James Hohenshell appeals a district court order denying his motion for a new trial and upholding a jury's award of damages. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
